<topic id="xslt-quick-assist">
  <title>XSLT Quick Assist Support</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Editing XSL Stylesheets<indexterm>quick assist support</indexterm></indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>The <term>Quick Assist</term> support helps you to rapidly access search and refactoring
      actions. If one or more actions are available in the current context, they are accessible via
      a yellow bulb help (<image href="../img/QuickAssist16.png"/>) placed at the current line in
      the stripe on the left side of the editor. Also, you can invoke the quick assist menu by using
      the  <uicontrol product="developer editor"><shortcut>Alt + 1</shortcut></uicontrol><uicontrol
        product="developerEclipse editorEclipse"><shortcut>Ctrl + 1</shortcut></uicontrol>
        (<uicontrol product="developer editor"><shortcut>Meta + Alt +
        1</shortcut></uicontrol><uicontrol product="developerEclipse editorEclipse"><shortcut>Meta
          1</shortcut></uicontrol> on Mac OS X) keyboard shortcuts.</p>
    <p>Two categories of actions are available in the <uicontrol>Quick Assist</uicontrol> menu:<ul
        id="ul_ckb_cfc_c4">
        <li>Actions available on a selection made inside an attribute that contains an XPath
            expression:<ul id="ul_eys_hfc_c4">
            <li>
              <uicontrol><image href="../img/CreateTemplate16.png" id="image_wlq_4fn_wr"/>Extract
                template</uicontrol> - <ph
                conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/extract_template_short_desc"/>
            </li>
            <li>
              <uicontrol><image href="../img/CreateStylesheet16.png" id="image_p2z_2fn_wr"/>Move to
                another stylesheet</uicontrol> - <ph
                conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/move_to_another_stylesheet_short_desc"/>
            </li>
            <li>
              <uicontrol>Extract local variable</uicontrol> - <ph
                conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/extract_local_var_sh_desc"/>
            </li>
            <li>
              <uicontrol>Extract global variable</uicontrol> - <ph
                conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/extract_global_var_sh_desc"/>
            </li>
            <li>
              <uicontrol>Extract template parameter</uicontrol> - <ph
                conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/extract_templ_param_sh_desc"/>
            </li>
            <li>
              <uicontrol>Extract global parameter</uicontrol> - <ph
                conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/extract_global_param_sh_desc"/>
            </li>
          </ul><fig id="fig_pmp_k3c_c4">
            <title>XSLT Quick Assist Support - Refactoring Actions</title>
            <image href="../img/xslt_quick_assist_refactoring_actions.png" id="image_jpc_43c_c4"
              product="developer editor"/>
            <image href="../img/ec_xslt_quick_assist_refactoring_actions.png" id="image_nqc_yjc_c4"
              product="developerEclipse editorEclipse"/>
          </fig></li>
        <li>actions available when the cursor is positioned over the name of a component:<dl
            conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/quick_assist_actions_list">
            <dlentry>
              <dt/>
              <dd/>
            </dlentry>
          </dl></li>
      </ul></p>
